1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Limited drops trigger a worldwide stampede the instant they go live.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Tickets and limited releases routinely oversell, double-book, and crash — and no one even knows who actually got one.

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:30,000
DROPZERO is a drop platform that never oversells, no matter how many millions hit it at once.

4
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Here's the app — built with v0 and deployed on Vercel.

5
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Stock updates in real time, and a purchase returns a confirmed order.

6
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:10,000
It speaks eight languages, with full right-to-left layout for Arabic.

7
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:18,000
Here's the heart of it — one single unit in stock.

8
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:30,000
We fire two purchases at the very same instant: one to Tokyo, one to Seoul — two different regions.

9
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Amazon Aurora DSQL's multi-region strong consistency means exactly one wins.

10
00:01:42,000 --> 00:02:10,000
Stock never goes negative, and both regions agree on the result.

11
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:22,000
Now let's scale it: a hundred units, and three thousand concurrent purchases across both regions.

12
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:36,000
The result — exactly one hundred confirmed, everything else sold out, zero errors.

13
00:02:36,000 --> 00:03:00,000
Thousands of buyers, and we sell precisely our stock — never one more.

14
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:09,000
Here's how it works. The frontend is on Vercel.

15
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:22,000
Auth uses OIDC federation to assume an AWS IAM role and mint a DSQL token — zero hardcoded secrets.

16
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:32,000
Each purchase checks and decrements stock in one transaction; concurrency conflicts are absorbed by retries.

17
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:40,000
This is only this clean because Aurora DSQL is multi-region and strongly consistent.

18
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:50,000
Zero oversell is fairness — against bots, against chaos.

19
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:56,000
Anywhere on earth, everyone sees one single source of truth.

20
00:03:56,000 --> 00:04:00,000
DROPZERO: global drops that never oversell.
